    "course_title": "ADVANCED ALGORITHMS",
    "description": "Advanced paradigms for the design and analysis of efficient algorithms, including the use of randomness, linear programming, and semi-definite programming. Applications to data structures, approximating NP-hard optimization problems, learning, on-line and distributed problems.  Students are strongly encouraged to have introductory knowledge of algorithms (e.g.,COMP\u00a0SCI\u00a0577)",
